    <item>
      <title>跳羚表示私募股权交易将推动赞助热潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/springboks-sa-rugby-say-private-equity-deal-to-fuel-sponsorship-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SA Rugby 负责管理卫冕世界冠军跳羚队，预计在一项计划中的私募股权交易的支持下，到 2027 年世界杯，其赞助收入将翻一番，该交易的商业权估值为 3.75 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/springboks-sa-rugby-say-private-equity-deal-to-fuel-sponsorship-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>调查显示，欧洲央行过早降息比推迟降息更糟糕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/ecb-cutting-too-soon-would-be-worse-than-delaying-survey-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项对经济学家的调查显示，对欧洲央行来说，过早降息比太晚降息更糟糕，他们预计 2024 年降息次数会减少。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-01/ecb-cutting-too-soon-would-be-worse-than-delaying-survey-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
